name: Salted Egg Yolk Flavor Chocolate
description: I'm not sure when it first started, but ever since that time, the salted egg yolk-flavored food craze has swept the world. It's as if everywhere I look is salted egg yolk. I try to my avert my eyes, but nothing but salted egg yolk awaits me. All of this makes me... unable to refuse.
usage: Edible product used to restore Sanity. Will be consumed upon receipt. Ready to eat.
